    About this hotel

    Set 2 km from Anna Park, this posh hillside hotel is 4 km from both Kiliyur Falls and the scenic views at Lady's Seat.…

    Featuring balconies with pool views, the polished rooms have free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, as well as minifridges, and tea and coffeemaking equipment; some offer exposed-stone accent walls. Upgraded rooms provide valley views; some have whirlpool tubs. Room service is available.

    A breakfast buffet and parking are included. Amenities consist of a hip bar/lounge, and a bright tri-level restaurant with floor-to-ceiling windows. There’s a gym and a terrace, along with a glass skywalk, and an outdoor pool with jungle views.

    Check-in time: 14:00
    Check-out time: 12:00
